Frank Wood (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Wood_(actor) 0 Frank Wood (born March 1960) is an American actor who has appeared in various television, film, and theatre roles. His most frequent role was performing as Greg in the HBO series Flight Of The Conchords.
